{"tid":1391673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"生存遊戲防彈大法(有片佐證) & 水槍戰術討論","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:41:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T14:18:07.000Z","uid":170423,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39411775d09a05ab6d066b9844f46e14fa537ae9","tid":1391673,"uid":170423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:41:21.000Z","msg":"本文用途只在於學術討論生存遊戲，還請各位讀者切勿對號入座 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本文要點:<br />\n1)如何製作生存遊戲所用嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>防彈衣</strong></span><br />\n2)如何對付生存遊戲中坐車拎住支<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大水槍</span></strong>嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">1)如何製作生存遊戲所用嘅防彈衣</span></em></strong><br />\n防彈衣係生存遊戲中不可或缺，因為佢可以減輕你身體比BB彈射中嘅痛感，如果有時放工臨時想去玩一場game或者鍾意自己DIY生存遊戲裝備嘅話，咁呢個post一定啱你！<br />\n首先希望大家睇睇段片(0:40-4:00):<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jEPt1pfj0Bc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjEPt1pfj0Bc&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=703e7012\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jEPt1pfj0Bc</a><br />\n片入面就用咗10塊<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">2.5cm-3cm厚嘅磨刀石</span></em>排兩排再用膠紙黐實制作而成，至於點解片入面會黐多兩本書就係因為佢想拎返啲子彈。大家可以見到片入面件自製防彈衣可以擋到.357麥格農子彈，根據返維基百科(<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/.357%E9%BA%A5%E6%A0%BC%E8%BE%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F.357%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E6%25A0%25BC%25E8%25BE%25B2&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=dcc5f2eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/.357%E9%BA%A5%E6%A0%BC%E8%BE%B2</a>)，就算係最廢嘅.357麥格農子彈能量都有<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><ins>778J</ins></strong></span>，足足係平常BB彈槍嘅700幾倍，可以想像下同時有700人開槍射你都唔驚，更莫講平時生存遊戲見到嘅Nerf衝鋒槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n好處:<br />\n－方便製作，用紙皮做底+膠紙黐實就得<br />\n－拆裝容易，如果完game要返屋企可以逐塊拆返走，方便運送<br />\n壞處:<br />\n－重，都有成4kg<br />\n－動作會無咁靈活<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2)如何對付生存遊戲中坐車拎住支大水槍嘅人</span></em></strong><br />\n香港可能少見啲，外國啲生存遊戲中有時有啲人會玩水戰，佢哋國家土地多，有場可以拎住水槍渣住車係個大場射，但啲外國人就係鍾意加啲難度比自己，例如啲水槍專員淨係可以固定係車上面冇得走，咁如果大家有幸出國玩呢啲另類生存遊戲可以點？<br />\n<br />\nA)即刻走啦仲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nB)搵啲嘢阻住呢啲載水槍專員嘅車，因為有時佢哋啲車又慢又唔靈活<br />\nC)兜去車後面盲點位<br />\n<br />\n以上就係小弟對於生存遊戲嘅一啲看法，重申一次小弟打呢段文只係想學術討論一下，大家歡迎留言討論下啲可能性呀之類～"},{"pid":"9c89cb27d278892847da01efca6b4469d1476bd6","tid":1391673,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與罷工罷市罷課<br />\n<br />\n8月2日 公務員罷工集會<br />\n8月5日 一齊罷工 7區集會"},{"pid":"b12277244ea042c17d3972478459a28af5a45b73","tid":1391673,"uid":170423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:44:44.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該開係學術台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad6e27a8d2c5b16cdf6abc903537528f2472b46","tid":1391673,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eebe2f9a24e5cc47046759a1fdafa6ff5d44c5e","tid":1391673,"uid":276834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:46:19.000Z","msg":"有時見到瑜伽磚的物料覺得幾輕身都防撞，唔知可唔可以賭黎整輕身version 呢&hellip;"},{"pid":"1bbde39f1b3de326460e76dfdf7f13958c6410c6","tid":1391673,"uid":170423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bad6e27a8d2c5b16cdf6abc903537528f2472b46","tid":1391673,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786fcf6778d9ee38595c9f49cd1eea6091158306","tid":1391673,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DErY1NGl2p_M&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=53147671\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ErY1NGl2p_M</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwGX_Vgq-1G0&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFiPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=0339c6ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港！時代革命！<br />\nLiberate Hong Kong! <br />\nThe Revolution Of Our Times! </span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>五大訴求</strong></span></span></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><ins>Hongkongers 5 Demands:</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n1. Full Withdrawal of the Extradition Bill<br />\n2. Retraction of the Characterisation of the Protestas a Riot<br />\n3. Release all Arrested Protesters<br />\n4. Accountability for Police and Yuen Long White Shirts Brutality<br />\n5. Implement Dual Universal Suffrage<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/Rcba2Hh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRcba2Hh.png&h=a61a5d44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fm6yf2o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffm6yf2o.jpg&h=67e4b0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時間無多，政府拖字訣，想我地自亂陣腳，行動規模必須升級</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dcb6a7fe7a4a18c176429d3d674e0808e57895f","tid":1391673,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bbde39f1b3de326460e76dfdf7f13958c6410c6","tid":1391673,"uid":170423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bad6e27a8d2c5b16cdf6abc903537528f2472b46","tid":1391673,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}